name: Tiffany and Jae
coverLetter: Been trimming and working harvest for the past few months in Cali, this is my first year, my partner Jae has been in the scene for 7yrs, I usually trim about 2lbs a day, working with my partner we get about 4 to 5lbs a day, will be back in Oregon the end of December looking for shelter for myself, my partner and 3 pups from Jan and beyond, we go where the work is.
